<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c4">[التَّسَلُّب]</span>: تسلبت المرأة على الميت:<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>أي لبست السِّلاب، ومنه<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>الحديث <span class="c2">«٢»</span>:<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c2">«تسلَّبي ثلاثاً ثم اصنعي ما شئت»</span><a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
